cast.overview: Paul Atreides, a brilliant and gifted young man born into a great destiny beyond his understanding, must travel to the most dangerous planet in the universe to ensure the future of his family and his people. As malevolent forces explode into conflict over the planet's exclusive supply of the most precious resource in existence-a commodity capable of unlocking humanity's greatest potential-only those who can conquer their fear will survive.
cast.title: Dune

details.biography: Charlie Rawes hails from England. He was a design student during 1997 at Colchester Institute. Represented by the Gregg Millard Management in London, England, Rawes began his acting career in 2011. His early credits often included playing brawny, nasty and tough characters. His film credits include Gangsters, Guns & Zombies (2012), Skiptrace (2016), King Arthur: Legend of the Sword (2017) and Jurassic World: Fallen Kingdom (2018). Charlie Rawes has experience as a presenter and voice actor.
details.name: Charlie Rawes
